{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, choose one of your opponent's creatures and destroy. Then choose a card from your opponent's mana zone and put it into its owner's graveyard.
■ Whenever your opponent puts a card into their graveyard from anywhere, you may put the top card of your deck into your mana zone.

{MACH FIGHTER} (This creature can attack tapped or untapped creatures on the turn you put it.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ Whenever this creature attacks, put the top card of your deck into your mana zone. Then you may return a card from your mana zone to your hand.

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. Put any number of Dragon creatures from among them into your hand and put the rest into your mana zone tapped.
■ Once per turn, you may summon a Dragon creature from your mana zone. (Pay the cost.)

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. Put any number of Dragon creatures from among them into your hand and put the rest into your mana zone tapped.
■ Once per turn, you may summon a Dragon creature from your mana zone. (Pay the cost.)
